## LESSONS LEARNED

Before touching any file that involves UI layout, Zustand stores, navigation, or animations,
check LESSONS_LEARNED.md for relevant prior bugs and patterns.

When a session produces a new hard-won lesson (unexpected bug, surprising platform behavior,
tooling quirk), add it to LESSONS_LEARNED.md before committing. Format:
- Short title
- Date discovered + file
- What happened (plain English)
- The fix or rule going forward

